	<span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted in</span><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20230621052936/https://vtdigger.org/category/government-politics/" rel="category tag">Government &amp; Politics</a></span>			<h1 class="entry-title ">
