<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow"><div class="widget widget_nav_menu"><h2 class="widgettitle">Counties</h2><div class="menu-footer-menu-three-container"><ul id="menu-footer-menu-three" class="menu"><li id="menu-item-540989" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-540989"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20230621052936/https://vtdigger.org/category/regional/champlain-valley/addison-county/">Addison</a></li>
